data.description:
221 Red Barn is a 4-bedroom home with a double-car attached garage, a double-car detached shop, RV Parking, and nearly a half-acre lot! Bring your toys, your hobbies, and your friends! 

A unique offering, this property has just completed a significant remodel. It boasts a new 30-year roof on the house and shop (installed in September of 2023), new laminate and carpet, fresh paint, new hardware, and light and bright windows! 

The home lives easily as a single-level or two-story home, with the upstairs bonus room serving as a 4th bedroom or flex space. This gem stands out as a nearly new home, and the loving care of the remodel sets it apart from its competitors.
